# Context7 integration

When the user asks about:
- Library APIs or documentation
- Framework setup or configuration (e.g. React, Next.js)
- Code examples for external packages
- How to use a specific library feature

Use Context7 MCP to fetch current documentation. Don't rely on training data for library-specific code.

For React: use context7 for React, or use context7 for React 18 when version matters.
